  "title": "Admin Assistant / Registration Clerk #76016",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Maritime</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Admin Assistant / Registration Clerk</strong></li><li>Working Location: City Hall</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days, Mon - Fri (9.00am - 5.30pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic up to $3000 + AWS + Performance Bonus + Yearly Increment</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare and submit documents for vessel registration.</li><li>Communicate and coordinate with ship owners, ship managers, lawyers, banks, and financial institutions.</li><li>Maintain accurate and up-to-date registration records.</li><li>Provide administrative support including scheduling and file management.</li><li>Respond to inquiries regarding vessel registration processes.</li><li>Other duties assigned by management.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Maritime Business / Business Admin or equivalent.</li><li>Experience in an administrative role, maritime industry experience preferred.</li><li>Proficiency in MS Office and database management.</li><li>Individuals without experience are encouraged to apply, training is provided.</li><li></li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#76016 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
